data.name: lblDirection2.Text
data.value: Click on a colored marble at the bottom as a choice, and then click on a button in the currently active row to change the color to the selected marble. When you have your guess ready, press the check button to check your answer.

data.name: lblDirection3.Text
data.value: If the entered guess is incorrect, the game will display a hint to the side of the previously answered row. Colors for the hint are: red - the right color in the right spot white - the right color in the wrong spot black - the wrong color Red always goes before white regardless of the position of the colors in your guess.
